{"tid":624628,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"比基諷皇馬歐冠好籤：我都想踢他們","createTime":"2018-04-10T23:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T00:18:26.000Z","uid":45952,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"450159e34c8e005dcc8764f5c4bf6ce46313342e","tid":624628,"uid":45952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:28:32.000Z","msg":"新浪網 2016-08-25 08:05:19<br />\n<br />\n比基不會放過任何一個諷刺死敵皇馬的機會。在Twitter上與網民進行問答互動時，這位巴塞中堅暗示皇馬上季歐冠盃奪冠時的簽運太好。<br />\n　　香港時間明天淩晨，新賽季歐冠盃小組賽抽籤儀式就將舉行。在被問到希望碰到的對手時，比基說：「我更喜歡一個簡單點的小組，希望16強踢意甲的第3名，8強踢德甲的第8名，4強踢英超的第4名，而且全都是先客後主。」<br />\n　　感覺很熟悉？比基這番話無疑是在諷刺皇馬。上季歐冠盃，皇馬一路獲得冠軍，他們小組賽的對手是巴黎聖日耳門、薩克達、馬模，淘汰賽前三個對手分別是羅馬、禾夫斯堡和曼城，也就是比基口中的意甲第4、德甲第8和英超第4。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/6218413/85/20160825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F6218413%2F85%2F20160825&d=6xk%2F9XeIPJjZF1upQV6olQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=c0dd85de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/6218413/85/20160825</a><br />\n<br />\nOk 你都抽到啦，開心？"},{"pid":"9c56816dd82c9694109968081c0ccc38b1bfd18c","tid":624628,"uid":137605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d57f170825ac9e836d9494acdc08dc120bdfd0c","tid":624628,"uid":18669,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:32:39.000Z","msg":"以後仲有臉笑皇抽羅馬？"},{"pid":"d2393e9b164443616af6bb844f0124380d369197","tid":624628,"uid":23809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d257b302e9ec044ca5adeb37d81b12dee87435","tid":624628,"uid":25345,"like